title: Rachael vs. Guy Celebrity Cook Off - Season 2 Complete
description:
Rachael vs. Guy: Celebrity Cook-Off is an American cooking competition series on the Food Network. The series pits Team Captains Rachael Ray and Guy Fieri against each other in determining who is the best cooking mentor toward their team of four celebrities. Each week, one celebrity will be eliminated, with the "last star standing" winning a $50,000.00 cash donation toward their charity.


The celebrities for season two will be Chilli, Gilbert Gottfried, Cornelia Guest, Dean McDermott, Kathy Najimy, Hines Ward, Carnie Wilson, and Johnny Weir.



Original Air Dates: 06-Jan-2013 to 10-Feb-2013
